{{Unlicensed}}The [[Green Galaxy]] was a glowing green [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] drink that had swirling bursts of light which looked much like [[Star/Legends|stars]]. It was served in tall drinking utensils. The [[Ravaging Wardog Cantina]] served these drinks during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

